{"type": "article", "id": 7231, "title": "Mollo 沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-10T07:53:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234156UqPc94bmQRVXOIuh.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tPhilippe Malouin 最近简直是椅子设计界的名人，此前<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/display/articles/1000.html\" target=\"_blank\">《好奇心日报》介绍过他的可折叠可悬挂椅子</a>，不知道你还记不记得。去年他还做了一款超软的沙发，就是下图你看到的这个。这个没有骨架，看起来肥肥的沙发名字叫做 Mollo，沙发由聚苯乙烯泡沫塑料做成，没有任何硬邦邦的内部支撑物，人们在上面可以随意调整姿势，寻找最舒适的体验。 <a href=\"http://establishedandsons.com/buy/\" target=\"_blank\">Established &amp; Sons 官网提供购买信息</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234153vMJnVPyBk9gbQp2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341532FYJNdu8jKZ0PfDt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234154gePyp2vZJ5lbkVBE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.23201856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234154vgnOA9xcNCewQjyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.31718062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234155YmzS8awyqvOnitX1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.25333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}